      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptional vehicle, maintained to an uncompromising standard. This example remains in showroom condition, exhibiting no discernible wear and reflecting a history of meticulous stewardship. For the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing short of perfection, this unit represents a rare opportunity to acquire a truly peerless automotive asset.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
